{
  "stem": "13600.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And night job, this I-- this I kept till I-- till I left Russia on the way back to Poland, by the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I slept there at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A place on the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two jobs, and I don't remember being hungry anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the bad times during the worst time of the war, the constant nagging thought was, where do I get something to eat?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well at that time I wasn't interested in not listening to their propaganda.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their propaganda was my hope for surviving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to come in the middle of the day in the library.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to take the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, not at Tashkent's, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lunachowsk's. ?] This is--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I used to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides, in the street were loudspeakers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to give the news, what happens, what the situation is in the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had an idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember by the way, the first time-- that was the end of the war, of course.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was in August '45.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was sitting here reading the paper, that Americans dropped a bomb that was 20,000 ton, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the force of 20,000 ton of TNT.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to myself, this must be a mistake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A bomb is 5,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the first atom bomb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh the newspapers was the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russian newspapers all [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] propaganda, propaganda, and propaganda.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you got a little bit of brain, you have just to understand and decide for yourself what is true and what is not true.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But mostly, the situation, the front you could visualize.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
